Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:47.22,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(120,0)}Wake up say it again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:50.28,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}Who have said dream never lie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:56.29,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}震えてた時へ繋がる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:59.62,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}そうさ君も全てを賭けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:02.77,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}戦う場所へ飛び出したら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:03.99,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}You can beat it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:08.82,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}さあさ Ready！After me！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:11.85,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}When the note was wrote so many
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:15.10,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}NO we still need to break the way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:22.74,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}見失ったものが青い気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.74,0:23:24.30,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,0)}We've better let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:26.03,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,0)}SELF! Ask youself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:27.47,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}WALK! 君と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:30.47,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}あの日のリズムを今に刻む
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.21,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(120,0)}YES! We should go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:36.77,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}WALK！ 遥か遠くに見てた未来を掴んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:38.32,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}Let's breath the fresh field
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:39.88,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}I can get you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:42.97,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}溢れたノイズを掻き鳴らす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:48.43,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}未来図は泡のように
